---
---

<section id="research" class="section research-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>AI Research</h2>
      <div class="section-line"></div>
    </div>
    <p class="lead">
      Deep learning has achieved remarkable results, but current architectures are hitting fundamental limits.
      We believe the path forward lies in mathematics—specifically in understanding the geometric structure of data
      and the symmetries that govern learning.
    </p>
    <p class="lead">
      Fractal Manifold is a research lab focused on advancing deep learning through rigorous mathematical foundations.
      We work at the intersection of differential geometry, group theory, and neural network design to build models
      that are not just bigger, but fundamentally better.
    </p>

    <div class="features">
      <article class="feature">
        <svg class="bg-icon" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2" />
          <rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6" />
          <path d="M9 1v3M15 1v3M9 20v3M15 20v3M1 9h3M1 15h3M20 9h3M20 15h3" />
        </svg>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>Advanced Deep Learning</h3>
          <p>Developing next-generation neural architectures</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="feature">
        <svg class="bg-icon" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1" />
          <path d="M20.2 20.2c2.04-2.03.02-7.36-4.5-11.9-4.54-4.52-9.87-6.54-11.9-4.5-2.04 2.03-.02 7.36 4.5 11.9 4.54 4.52 9.87 6.54 11.9 4.5z" />
          <path d="M15.7 15.7c4.52-4.54 6.54-9.87 4.5-11.9-2.03-2.04-7.36-.02-11.9 4.5-4.52 4.54-6.54 9.87-4.5 11.9 2.03 2.04 7.36.02 11.9-4.5z" />
        </svg>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>Fundamental Research</h3>
          <p>Exploring the theoretical foundations of artificial intelligence</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="feature">
        <svg class="bg-icon" aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z" />
        </svg>
        <div class="feature-content">
          <h3>Practical Applications</h3>
          <p>Transferring research insights into real-world solutions</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .feature {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(243, 158, 11, 0.1);
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  @media (hover: hover) {
    .feature:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      border-color: rgba(243, 158, 11, 0.35);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(243, 158, 11, 0.08);
    }
  }

  .bg-icon {
    position: absolute;
    width: 8rem;
    height: 8rem;
    opacity: 0.18;
    right: -1rem;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .feature-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .feature h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .feature p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
